Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.06,0:00:05.31,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Within the spreading darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.40,0:00:08.02,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I pledged a vow to the revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.15,0:00:13.20,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I can't let anybody interrupt it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.28,0:00:18.33,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'm going to change
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.83,0:00:31.09,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The future that the forbidden fruit foretells...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.30,0:00:39.51,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'm going to change the dream into reality
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.27,0:00:51.40,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The ending that everybody wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.36,0:00:54.70,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Within the spreading darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.74,0:00:57.45,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I pledged our vow to the revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.53,0:01:02.33,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I can't let anybody interrupt it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.49,0:01:07.79,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Someday I'll show you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.79,0:01:17.09,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}A bright and ideal world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.57,0:01:36.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised, Ryuga.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.32,0:01:38.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought that you'd\Nsuddenly ask me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.95,0:01:40.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,to play some tennis to get\Nto know each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.74,0:01:42.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.58,0:01:44.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.12,0:01:46.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say that already knowing\Nmy abilities?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.62,0:01:49.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.17,0:01:53.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was once the British Junior Champion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.71,0:01:56.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I ask him if he's British,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.55,0:01:59.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,would he think that I'm trying to find out\Nmore about him because I'm Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.72,0:02:01.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. I'll give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.39,0:02:03.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuga, were you raised in Britain?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.64,0:02:07.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I lived in Britain for five years, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.48,0:02:12.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. There's nothing there\Nthat can reveal L's identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.61,0:02:14.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.19,0:02:19.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the first to win a set or\Nsix games wins the game, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.16,0:02:20.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.12,0:02:30.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just a friendly game of tennis.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.21,0:02:33.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a test to determine\Nif Light is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.63,0:02:37.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But Kira hates to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.97,0:02:47.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fifteen, love.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:51.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, Ryuga.\NYou're serious right from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:53.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The person who makes the first move wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.82,0:02:56.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean that you can't say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.11,0:02:58.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.40,0:03:00.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Under L's orders,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.45,0:03:03.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,no one outside the task force can know,\Neven you, Deputy Director General.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.66,0:03:06.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even what you are doing and\Nwhere you're doing it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:08.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:13.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.17,0:03:18.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been more than four months since\Nthis case has come to light.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.01,0:03:22.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,People are saying that\Nthe police and L are incompetent...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:24.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,With all due respect, Sir, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:26.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you really call the police\Ncompetent for
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.01,0:03:28.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,putting their tails between\Ntheir legs in fear of Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.18,0:03:33.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You should see how many people\Nare left at task force headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.85,0:03:35.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're worried about\Nwhat people are saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.56,0:03:37.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,then try not to let them know that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.44,0:03:40.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the bulk of the detectives\Nhave run away from Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.86,0:03:43.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.57,0:03:46.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.20,0:03:51.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What about L?\NCan he be trusted?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.87,0:03:55.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think he's much more\Ncapable than we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.25,0:03:59.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's putting his life at\Nstake right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.89,0:04:07.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they really amateurs?\NWho are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.39,0:04:10.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're Light Yagami and\NHideki Ryuga.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.06,0:04:13.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The two who entered\Nthis year with top scores.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:18.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Yagami.\NKira hates to lose, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.73,0:04:21.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Most people don't like to lose.\NIt's not just Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:25.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is getting worked up and going\Nfor the win something Kira would do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.16,0:04:28.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, if I lose on purpose,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:31.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he'll think that getting worked up\Nand winning is like Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.24,0:04:34.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so losing on purpose is\Nalso like Kira... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.58,0:04:36.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end,\Nit's the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:40.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that he would\Nprofile me with this tennis game.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.13,0:04:43.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He has some other goal in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.76,0:04:46.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But even if it is just tennis...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.93,0:04:47.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I will win!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.73,0:04:55.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See, you came in for the win.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.27,0:04:58.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Game count, four games all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.61,0:05:01.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All of a sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:04.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,there's an umpire and a line judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:05.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.78,0:05:09.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd heard of Light Yagami\Nsomewhere, so I looked him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.87,0:05:12.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems he was the Junior High Champion\Nin 2002 and 2003.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.04,0:05:14.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,During the Junior High third-year\Ncommendation ceremony...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.96,0:05:16.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he announced that he'd only\Nplay in junior high.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.17,0:05:19.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't played in\Nany tournaments since.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:20.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:23.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So what about Ryuga?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.38,0:05:25.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's holding his own with\Nthe junior high champion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:31.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can read your feelings,\NLight Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:35.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that this kind of tennis\Ncan deepen our friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.85,0:05:37.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just going through\Nthe motions...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.14,0:05:39.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just so we can say\Nwe're better friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.81,0:05:42.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,By playing tennis with you,\Nyou will think...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:47.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that I am preparing to take a step\Ncloser to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.74,0:05:50.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And then you're gonna try to\Nget me to say something...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.07,0:05:53.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,only Kira would know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:57.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you'll tell me you'll need to know\Nif you can trust me first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.00,0:06:00.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And try to get me to give you details\Non the Kira case...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:03.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I want to talk about\Nthe Kira case...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.13,0:06:07.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to have to ask\Nhim for proof
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.63,0:06:11.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that he's currently in charge of\Nthe Kira Case.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.01,0:06:15.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So the first thing you're going to\Nwant out of me is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.31,0:06:20.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,proof that you really are L\Nfrom a third party.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.10,0:06:22.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.52,0:06:24.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- we'll go to the task force headquarters!\N- we'll go to the task force headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.44,0:06:28.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In life, one cannot win\Njust by playing defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.86,0:06:30.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To win...\NYou need to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.53,0:06:36.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Game set. Won by Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.70,0:06:38.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Six games to four!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:40.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.63,0:06:46.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As I expected of you. I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.84,0:06:49.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuga, It's been a while since\NI've played seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.72,0:06:51.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.18,0:06:54.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And I have something I want\Nto ask you,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.22,0:06:55.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so do you want to go\Nget a drink afterwards?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.26,0:07:00.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've lost the game,\Nso I'll tell you whatever I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.39,0:07:04.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But before that,\NI have something I must tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.44,0:07:06.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:11.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami, I suspect that you,\Nare Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:14.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you still want to ask me,\Ngo ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.58,0:07:20.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.25,0:07:23.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, even though I say\NI suspect you,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.67,0:07:24.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,it's only a one-percent possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:26.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Leaving that aside,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.63,0:07:28.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,once I'm sure that you aren't Kira and
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:32.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,because you have\Nsharp reasoning abilities,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.43,0:07:35.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like for you to work with me\Non this investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.18,0:07:40.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,One-percent, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.14,0:07:42.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's well-worded.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.81,0:07:45.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he suspects me\Njust a little,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.81,0:07:47.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,it still means that it won't do\Nany good
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:49.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,if I ask him to meet\Nsomeone from the task force.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.69,0:07:51.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means he beat me\Nto the punch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.74,0:07:53.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He beat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.20,0:07:59.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This coffee shop is\None of my favorites.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:03.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we sit here, there's no chance\Nof anyone overhearing us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.92,0:08:05.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a nice spot you've shown me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:10.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have to worry about\Nhow we sit here either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.46,0:08:14.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to sit like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.84,0:08:19.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I sit normally, my reasoning skills\Ndrop by forty percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.18,0:08:22.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So...what did you want to ask me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.18,0:08:23.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.31,0:08:26.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That can wait until\Nyou're sure that I'm not Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.44,0:08:29.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can talk about whatever\Nyou want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.65,0:08:35.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then excuse me but, do you mind\Nif I test your deductive skills?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.95,0:08:39.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, okay. Sounds like fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.74,0:08:43.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then first...please take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.83,0:08:49.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,These three are pictures of notes that\Nwe believe were written
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.05,0:08:53.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,by criminals in prison right before they died,\Nwhile under Kira's.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:57.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell me what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.10,0:09:01.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.72,0:09:04.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, what a childish trick...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:07.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The print number is written on\Nthe back of these photographs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.36,0:09:09.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I paid no attention to this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:16.40,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(309,88)}L DO YOU KNOW
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:16.40,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(121,250)\frz3.883}GODS OF DEATH
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:13.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And correctly unscrambled\Nthe sentence the way Kira wrote it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.03,0:09:16.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"L do you know,\NGods of Death love apples..."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.74,0:09:18.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There'd be a strong possibility that\NI'd be Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:24.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But just because I solve this code\Ndoesn't prove I'm Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.92,0:09:31.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be amazing if Kira\Ncould not only inflict death on others,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.04,0:09:32.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but control his victims actions\Nas well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.21,0:09:37.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And there's a message encoded here\Ntaunting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:41.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When we rearrange the messages and\Ntake a look at the top letters of each line,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.97,0:09:43.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,they form another sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.72,0:09:46.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rearranging it into a message\Nwhich makes sense would probably be...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.56,0:09:53.07,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(362,81)}L DO YOU KNOW
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.56,0:09:53.07,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(402,206)}GODS OF DEATH
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.56,0:09:53.07,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(372,353)}LOVE APPLES
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.10,0:09:52.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"L, do you know?\NGods of Death love apples."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.57,0:09:56.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But there are print numbers in the back...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.90,0:09:58.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When we arrange them in that order...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.32,0:10:04.29,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(366,102)}L DO YOU KNOW
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.32,0:10:04.29,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(373,218)}LOVE APPLES
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.32,0:10:04.29,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(394,332)}GODS OF DEATH
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.82,0:10:03.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We get, "L, do you know?\NLove Apples, Gods of Death"...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:07.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't make sense and\Nit's hard to think that
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.25,0:10:09.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira would have wanted you\Nto read it this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.75,0:10:11.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Incorrect.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:15.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are actually\Nfour photographs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:18.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When we add this one,\Nthis is what it reads...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.47,0:10:24.64,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz356.865\pos(365,223)}HAVE RED HANDS
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.63,0:10:24.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"L, do you know? Gods of Death who\Nlove apples have red hands."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.22,0:10:29.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a fake. This fourth picture is not\Na message I made a criminal write.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:31.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.23,0:10:35.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But even with the three photographs,\Nmy deduction was perfect, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.94,0:10:37.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:39.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is that there\Nare four of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.82,0:10:41.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It would have been perfect if\Nyou'd figured out there was another.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.78,0:10:46.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami, even though you knew\Nthe message wasn't finished,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.83,0:10:48.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you decided that there were\Nonly three notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.37,0:10:50.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't guess that there was a fourth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:52.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is also true...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.63,0:10:53.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn him...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.09,0:10:57.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. He isn't just gauging\Nmy deductive abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:10:59.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's trying to get me to reveal myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.38,0:11:02.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I latch onto this,\NI'll play right into his hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.09,0:11:06.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... I hadn't thought that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.18,0:11:10.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever the case,\Nit's not a message that would lead to Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.31,0:11:12.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gods of Death don't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.31,0:11:19.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then if you were me, faced with\Nsomeone who might be Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.65,0:11:21.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,how would you check\Nif he was Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.24,0:11:24.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I would try to have him say\Nsomething
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.49,0:11:27.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that wasn't broadcast to the public,\Nthat only Kira would know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:30.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What you were doing just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.71,0:11:32.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.87,0:11:36.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've asked several detectives\Nthat same question,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.29,0:11:39.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but most of them needed\Na few minutes to answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.63,0:11:40.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.01,0:11:45.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you immediately thought of a scenario\Nin which Kira is talking to the investigator.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.14,0:11:49.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your deductive abilities are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.19,0:11:56.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The more impressive my answers,\Nthe more of a suspect I become, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.11,0:11:59.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. By about three percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.94,0:12:04.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But in that respect, it's made me\Nmore determined to work with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.74,0:12:08.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you are Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:12.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like for us to work together\Non this investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.54,0:12:15.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.92,0:12:19.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I cooperate with you,\Nthe investigation will move forward,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.13,0:12:22.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and if I really am Kira,\NI might reveal myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.84,0:12:26.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, conduct the investigation\Nwhile investigating me all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.39,0:12:28.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's a great idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.81,0:12:31.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But aren't you getting\Nthe wrong idea, Ryuga?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.73,0:12:36.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm interested in the Kira case and\Nconduct detective work as a hobby, but..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.56,0:12:40.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not Kira,\Nand I don't want him to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.48,0:12:44.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, I have no proof\Nthat you aren't Kira, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:49.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be strange for just\None of us to be investigated, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.87,0:12:52.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither of us have proof\Nthat we aren't Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:57.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But Ryuga, if you are L,\NI'm sure you can show me proof of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.92,0:13:00.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Like having someone in the task force\Nor my father
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.88,0:13:03.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,tell me that you are really L\Nin person.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.76,0:13:07.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't,\NI can't investigate with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:11.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You talk a lot, don't you,\NLight Yagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.97,0:13:13.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Typical for someone who hates\Nto lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.10,0:13:17.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven percent... could he really be?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.27,0:13:21.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I never said that\NI wouldn't let you meet anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.73,0:13:23.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,from the task force headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.94,0:13:29.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am currently working\Nwith your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.62,0:13:35.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I take you to headquarters,\Nyou'll help with the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.62,0:13:38.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.79,0:13:41.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:46.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.26,0:13:48.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.26,0:13:50.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.14,0:13:53.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki, something terrible\Nhas happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:55.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, your father has...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:56.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.06,0:14:00.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My father had...a heart attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.95,0:14:16.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.54,0:14:18.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring your things that you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.71,0:14:20.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, I leave the rest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.00,0:14:21.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.38,0:14:29.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're sure it's just fatigue, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.01,0:14:34.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. When I collapsed,\NI thought it was Kira, but I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.06,0:14:37.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been pushing myself\Na bit hard lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.73,0:14:42.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially since your son\Nhas been suspected of being Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.15,0:14:44.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've told that to my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.90,0:14:45.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.82,0:14:49.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've told him everything.\NEven the fact that I'm L.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:54.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. He's L.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.24,0:14:59.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We call him Ryuzaki so others\Ncan't find out,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.91,0:15:01.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but there's no mistaking it. He is L.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.33,0:15:05.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the real L.\NMy father is telling me so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.88,0:15:08.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably the same L who has\Nbeen ordering the police until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:12.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I get rid of him and\Nthe investigative team...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.09,0:15:15.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's probably not\Nthat simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.51,0:15:19.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to rush.\NI'll have time to spy from here on...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.89,0:15:22.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.27,0:15:24.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to be the Light Yagami\Nwho is worried about his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.19,0:15:29.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So Ryuzaki, has talking\Nwith my son,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.11,0:15:30.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,cleared away your suspicions?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.53,0:15:34.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say that I suspect him,\Nbut it's only a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.37,0:15:37.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.58,0:15:41.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira killed twelve FBI agents\Nwho were in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.42,0:15:45.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They were tracking those who\Nwere connected to the Japanese police.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.54,0:15:48.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,One of them was Raye Penber...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.30,0:15:52.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There were many suspicious things\Nsurrounding his death.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:57.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And I was one of the people\Nhe was investigating.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.01,0:15:59.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no wonder I'm a suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.43,0:16:02.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's as Ryuga says...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.89,0:16:04.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no one else to suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.52,0:16:07.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your deductive ability\Nis quite impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.48,0:16:10.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's always quick and accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.90,0:16:13.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuga, I'll cooperate with you\Non this investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.82,0:16:17.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My father has vouched that you're L.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.03,0:16:22.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I want to catch Kira\Nand prove that I'm not him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.66,0:16:23.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.62,0:16:28.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon, you're going to have to study\Nto enter the police force.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:30.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be too late to\Ndo this afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.51,0:16:33.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:35.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how many years that'll take.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.39,0:16:40.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I promised you, didn't l?\NIf something happened to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.85,0:16:43.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be the one to\Nget Kira executed...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.19,0:16:48.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that\Nmy son can be Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.73,0:16:54.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to believe this is all an act.\NNo, if it is an act, it's too corny.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.66,0:16:58.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, listen to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.20,0:17:02.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact of the matter is... Kira is evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:06.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But recently, I've been thinking\Nabout it in this way-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.83,0:17:10.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The real evil is the power\Nto kill people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:15.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,People who attain\Nthat kind of power are unlucky...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.80,0:17:17.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how you use it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.89,0:17:23.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,nothing gained by killing people\Ncan bring true happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.18,0:17:25.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's as he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.69,0:17:30.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kira is an ordinary person\Nwho gained this power,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.48,0:17:33.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,then he is a very unlucky person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.32,0:17:36.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki, I'm sorry for\Ncausing you trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.86,0:17:39.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try to recover quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:40.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.45,0:17:43.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Visiting hours are now over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.17,0:17:52.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuga.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.05,0:17:56.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there any way that I can get\Nyou to believe that I'm not Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.43,0:18:01.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you aren't Kira, there wouldn't\Nbe any need to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:07.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut that out! Think about how\Nit feels to be accused of being Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.40,0:18:12.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.82,0:18:19.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How about keeping watch over me\Nin a place without even TV for a month?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.53,0:18:24.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Would someone really go\Nthat far to clear their name?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.08,0:18:25.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.20,0:18:29.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do anything which would\Ndeprive you of basic human rights.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.29,0:18:30.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And furthermore...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.50,0:18:33.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nonsense to take suggestions\Nfrom the suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.75,0:18:35.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.30,0:18:38.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.43,0:18:41.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll know in time if\Nyou're not Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.76,0:18:45.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, during that exchange\Nwith your father...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.85,0:18:47.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that you might not be Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.94,0:18:50.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, take care of your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.69,0:18:52.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.52,0:18:55.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I said that I would cooperate\Nwith the investigation,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.82,0:18:58.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't think I can do anything\Nuntil my father is well again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.82,0:19:00.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.66,0:19:02.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.66,0:19:08.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hideki Ryuga...Ryuzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.79,0:19:12.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the L I've been fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.42,0:19:14.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is his real name?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.84,0:19:20.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light Yagami...are you not Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.72,0:19:23.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuk...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.80,0:19:24.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.97,0:19:27.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I never once felt unlucky since
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.10,0:19:30.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I picked up this notebook\Nand gained this power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.27,0:19:35.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm wonderfully happy, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.82,0:19:37.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll create a wonderful world...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.65,0:19:45.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't care less if finding\Nthe notebook's made you happy or unlucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.24,0:19:47.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.08,0:19:50.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems people who have Shinigami\Nattached to them
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:52.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,experience nothing but misfortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.84,0:20:00.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I shall show you\Nan exception to the rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.22,0:20:03.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.26,0:20:10.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? Is this the only plan\Nyou can think of?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.14,0:20:11.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You think that we'll get ratings
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.48,0:20:15.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,if we do any special program\Non Kira, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.02,0:20:18.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been getting ratings
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.73,0:20:22.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,because we cover stories that\Nother stations don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.24,0:20:23.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.86,0:20:26.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The problem is with the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.66,0:20:28.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone bring me a good story!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.08,0:20:32.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But the police are keeping\Nquiet about this. It's hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.12,0:20:34.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.04,0:20:37.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't have any stories,\Njust make something up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.42,0:20:42.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Director Demegawa,\Na special delivery.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.80,0:20:45.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.22,0:20:47.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this from?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.85,0:20:57.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what I'm talking about.\NThis is what I want you to think of...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.61,0:21:00.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...this is just too good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.11,0:21:03.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"A message to the world from Kira."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.82,0:21:05.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"lf you don't broadcast this...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.86,0:21:08.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'll kill you all, starting from\Nyour company's president..."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.99,0:21:11.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who wouldn't air this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.74,0:21:14.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is amazing,\Nif it's real.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.25,0:21:19.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm so happy,\Nmy heart's racing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.26,0:21:28.18,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I dreamed a dream that no one could see,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.26,0:21:33.56,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I threw away everything that I didn't need
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.85,0:21:42.61,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I'm holding these feelings\Nthat I can't give up in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.73,0:21:48.99,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}Even if my feet fall victim\Nto the shackles of sacrifice
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.07,0:21:53.58,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}In between reality and my ideal
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.37,0:21:59.25,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I can't hold back the flooding impulses
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.33,0:22:06.72,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}Because I have a strong desire\Nto accomplish
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.30,0:22:11.89,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}[deceit] [fear] [vanity] [melancholy]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.01,0:22:22.65,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I'm not weak enough to believe\Nany of these negative perceptions
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.15,0:22:28.49,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I'm a trickster who doesn't know solitude
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.74,0:22:36.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I leave things the way they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.33,0:22:39.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L might be finished off\Nwithin the next four days.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.79,0:22:41.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,God is really on my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.71,0:22:45.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Only this time, it's not really God,\Nbut a Shinigami, a God of Death.
